## Request flow

```
GET /orders
    ↓
Identify tenant (header: x-tenant-id)
    ↓
Set AsyncLocalStorage tenant context
    ↓
<% if (model === 'multi-tenant-saas' && strategy === 'shared-db') { %>
Apply tenant_id filter on queries
<% } else if (model === 'multi-tenant-saas' && strategy === 'schema-per-tenant') { %>
Switch PostgreSQL schema dynamically
<% } else if (model === 'multi-tenant-saas' && strategy === 'db-per-tenant') { %>
Resolve dedicated DATABASE_URL for tenant
<% } else { %>
Use fixed default tenant
<% } %>
```

## Usage

```ts
import { registerTenancyMiddleware, getTenantId, bootstrapTenancy } from './src/tenancy/index.js';

await bootstrapTenancy();
await registerTenancyMiddleware(app);

app.get('/orders', async () => {
  const tenantId = getTenantId();
  // fetch orders scoped to tenantId
});
```

